l.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2186%2c20220929%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,簡,2186,20220929,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2186","JDATE":"20220929","JTITLE":"妨害電腦使用罪"}